{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1729093646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Runes of Aereal is a fast-paced, horror-themed roguelike deckbuilder set in the shadowy lands of Aereal. Build your deck, and blitz through enemies with a combination of combo-centric cards and items as you explore the land in search of the Runes of Immortality. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deckbuilder Meets an RPG</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/Cards_and_Crafting_Resized.gif?t=1729093646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Runes of Aereal combines deckbuilding and RPG elements- allowing players to choose from 6 characters with unique traits and abilities, making every playthrough immersive and unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Adventure Across the World of Aereal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/Map_Pan_Resized.gif?t=1729093646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the vast world of Aereal, visiting towns, unique locations and terrifying monstrosities- experiencing unique and rare events that mean no two runs are the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unlock New Combinations &amp; Grow Your Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/Deckbuilding_Resized.gif?t=1729093646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect new cards and magical items by slaying monsters, trading in cities, or, even, through Runes of Aereal\u2019s crafting system - transmuting mundane treasure into powe