ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/Map_Pan_Resized.gif?t=1729093646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the vast world of Aereal, visiting towns, unique locations and terrifying monstrosities- experiencing unique and rare events that mean no two runs are the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unlock New Combinations &amp; Grow Your Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/Deckbuilding_Resized.gif?t=1729093646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect new cards and magical items by slaying monsters, trading in cities, or, even, through Runes of Aereal\u2019s crafting system - transmuting mundane treasure into powerful scrolls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Bart Alluyn"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/header.jpg?t=1729093646","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257021933,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257021933/movie480.mp4?t=1715255241","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257021933/movie_max.mp4?t=1715255241"},"name":"Trailer May 2025","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257021933/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1715255241","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257021933/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1715255241","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.